19:53.368 --> 19:55.635
♪<i> and I owe it all to you</i> ♪

19:55.770 --> 20:00.773
♪<i> 'cause I've had</i>
<i> the time of my</i> ♪

20:00.775 --> 20:03.109
[ zapping, whooshing ]

20:03.111 --> 20:04.577
Raider dave!

20:04.713 --> 20:06.779
Wow!
All roads lead to raider dave.

20:06.915 --> 20:08.514
Well done, hayley.

20:08.516 --> 20:10.182
You looked wonderful
out there.

20:10.184 --> 20:11.384
[ glass shatters ]

20:11.386 --> 20:12.585
I've seen enough!

20:12.587 --> 20:14.387
I hereby
declare you

20:14.389 --> 20:17.790
"an adult woman"!

20:17.926 --> 20:19.125
This hamster
is yours.

20:19.127 --> 20:21.194
Hey, did my family
come to visit me

20:21.329 --> 20:22.529
While I was
in a coma?

20:22.664 --> 20:24.997
Hmm, no one told them,
I don't think?

20:24.999 --> 20:27.133
Haven't seen them in a while
if I'm being honest.

20:27.135 --> 20:29.836
Hayley!
Is it five minutes yet?

20:31.005 --> 20:32.939
No answer?
Really?

20:33.075 --> 20:35.709
I have to do everything
around here!

20:38.546 --> 20:39.946
"klaus, take out the trash!"

20:40.082 --> 20:41.748
"klaus, we're going
inside the new meat freezer

20:41.750 --> 20:43.884
For five minutes
to see if anyone gets cold!"

20:44.018 --> 20:46.819
"klaus, make sure you come
get us in five minutes!"

20:46.821 --> 20:47.954
Blah, blah, blah!

20:50.092 --> 20:52.292
Uh...So...

20:52.427 --> 20:54.127
Did anyone get cold?

20:55.029 --> 20:58.431
And I refuse
to take out the trash anymore!

20:58.433 --> 21:00.567
Have a great night!
